style # ::: section-content The style global attribute contains CSS styling declarations to be applied to the element. Note that it is recommended for styles to be defined in a separate file or files. This attribute and the &lt;style&gt; element have mainly the purpose of allowing for quick styling, for example for testing purposes. :::
